1. *Vaš* svet će biti pun sreće i uspeha. (Your world will be full of happiness and success.)

2. On je *vaš* prijatelj. (He is your friend.)

3. Šta je *vaš* plan? (What is your plan?)

4. Želim da znam *vaš* stav. (I want to know your opinion.)

5. *Vaš* nastup je bio impresivan. (Your performance was impressive.)

6. *Vaš* zadatak je da završite zadatak. (Your task is to finish the task.)

7. Gde je *vaš* dom? (Where is your home?)